Message.SourceString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.
Message.LocalizedString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.

Message.SourceString: I generally discourage violence, but this time I think you need to gather as much of it as possible and serve up a dragon sized portion.
Message.LocalizedString: I generally discourage violence, but this time I think you need to gather as much of it as possible and serve up a dragon sized portion.

Message.SourceString: Now then, an adventurer's work is never finished. Trust me, I know. There's a strange door to the north, just past Ashien's Watch and it's sending chills down my spine. Meet me there, we'll talk more.
Message.LocalizedString: Now then, an adventurer's work is never finished. Trust me, I know. There's a strange door to the north, just past Ashien's Watch and it's sending chills down my spine. Meet me there, we'll talk more.

Message.SourceString: There is an indention in the altar where something would be placed. It looks like it would fit the shape of Cathan's summoning horn design.
Message.LocalizedString: There is an indention in the altar where something would be placed. It looks like it would fit the shape of Cathan's summoning horn design.

Message.SourceString: The dragon's dead, that's quite the victory. No, really, you should be proud of yourself!
Message.LocalizedString: The dragon's dead, that's quite the victory. No, really, you should be proud of yourself!

Message.SourceString: It's not every day you take out a draconic general infused with the elemental power of the earth. But you managed it, well done!
Message.LocalizedString: It's not every day you take out a draconic general infused with the elemental power of the earth. But you managed it, well done!

Message.SourceString: We can relax for a little while, but not forever. Velgar was one tough cookie, but he's just the foot soldier. Queen Kuldra is out there somewhere and she won't sit quietly for long.
Message.LocalizedString: We can relax for a little while, but not forever. Velgar was one tough cookie, but he's just the foot soldier. Queen Kuldra is out there somewhere and she won't sit quietly for long.

Message.SourceString: Here, I'll take that rapidly decomposing head off you and give you something much better in return.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, I'll take that rapidly decomposing head off you and give you something much better in return.

Message.SourceString: What's that? Velgar's dead? Are you sure? I'll need to see his head, dragons can be tricky like that.
Message.LocalizedString: What's that? Velgar's dead? Are you sure? I'll need to see his head, dragons can be tricky like that.

Message.SourceString: Cathan's dead? To shreds you say? Poor lad, not the end he deserved. But Velgar's made a mistake here, he's made this personal.
Message.LocalizedString: Cathan's dead? To shreds you say? Poor lad, not the end he deserved. But Velgar's made a mistake here, he's made this personal.

Message.SourceString: Bring me his head and I'll make sure you're rewarded.
Message.LocalizedString: Bring me his head and I'll make sure you're rewarded.

Message.SourceString: There is an indention in the altar where something would be placed. It looks like it would fit the shape of Cathan's summoning horn design.
Message.LocalizedString: There is an indention in the altar where something would be placed. It looks like it would fit the shape of Cathan's summoning horn design.

Message.SourceString: OK... not sure why you want to keep a decomposing dragon's head around, but you do you I guess.
Message.LocalizedString: OK... not sure why you want to keep a decomposing dragon's head around, but you do you I guess.

Message.SourceString: There is an indentation in the altar where something would be placed, but you are not sure what it might be.
Message.LocalizedString: There is an indentation in the altar where something would be placed, but you are not sure what it might be.

Message.SourceString: Build the horn. Summon Velgar. Avenge Cathan, save us all. Punch a dragon in the face!
Message.LocalizedString: Build the horn. Summon Velgar. Avenge Cathan, save us all. Punch a dragon in the face!

Properties.TextName: Return to the Wise old man after killing velgar
